## Known Risks and Dependencies

| Risk | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| Example: Existing trigger on Account may conflict | Medium | Extend AccountTriggerHandler, don't add a new trigger |
| Example: Field-level security strips custom field for some profiles | High | Use System.runAs() in tests, add fieldPermissions in Permission Set |
| Example: External API rate limit | Low | Add retry logic in Queueable, log failures to custom object |

