## Test Strategy

| Test Class | Methods to Cover | Key Assertions |
|---|---|---|
| `FeatureNameServiceTest` | `processRecords` — positive, negative, bulk | Field values updated correctly, no exceptions thrown |
| `FeatureNameServiceTest` | `getDisplayData` — valid ID, null ID | Returns correct wrapper data, throws AuraHandledException on null |

**Bulk test:** Insert 200 `ObjectName__c` records and call `processRecords`. Assert all 200 are updated correctly.

**runAs requirement:** Yes — tests call `Security.stripInaccessible()`. Use a Standard User with the `FeatureName_Access` Permission Set.

